        (wppOpWhiskeredConcreteQuotientCoconeW506 X).ι.app ordinaryTargetIndexW478 by rfl]
  rw [show (wppOpWhiskeredConcreteQuotientCoconeW506 X).ι.app ordinaryTargetIndexW478 =
